extendedInfo.description: DELHI University's app is a free android app developed by Fgrouptech and is for Delhi University located in New Delhi , India. This app provide the view of official website on the android products . This app is designed to provided applicants and student with all information related to location, courses offered, admission,events, etc.The Delhi University App has the following features (currently):1. Easy and fast access to official portal.2. Detailed information on courses offered.3. Direct access to latest events/results. 4. University location at your finger tips.5. College list at a glance.5. Has emergency contact details of university and police.This app is free to use and is compatible with android 2.3+ devices. You can also share it with your friends.List of Colleges Affiliated to Delhi University-This is a list of colleges affiliated with Delhi University. reviews.title: Pretty Good! (Y)
reviews.comment: It\'s actually a pretty good app. Something that I wasn\'t really expecting from DU, considering how in the past the DU website has always been under scrutiny. The app is very convenient and works pretty fast too! It doesn\'t eat too much space too. All in all, it\'s a must-download app!
reviews.author: Cheshtha Gupta
